ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectParis Chamber of Commerce (Ontario) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the PARIS CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in Ontario, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the Town of Paris to the limits of the Town of Paris, and the municipality of the County of Brant except the City of Brantford.
